 />\n可能係我太認真，sor"},{"pid":"a436a758ce8af37b1ab28f4fe5530adf8763eb43","tid":497431,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T23:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恐怖分子會同人談判嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n唔係餐餐炸鳩完你跟手喺網上講嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n可能係我太認真，sor</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642a5872f295511ec06684c74de158f0232082a8","tid":497431,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>恐怖分子會同人談判嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n唔係餐餐炸鳩完你跟手喺網上講嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n可能係我太認真，sor</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7e8f95f99851f8c67aa5c9d9cbcd46e1b09e6","tid":497431,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"用李天命既思考藝術同佢對話"},{"pid":"24a2db2ddb80c8609159b48b1a9efaeb722bf7ca","tid":497431,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"一句Allahu Akbar就引爆架啦,邊到仲會有人講咁多野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b8fca33b4a50a772f8cea66bcb1455a0e8045e","tid":497431,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2675513edf3f470315535777082e7a73f6945577","tid":497431,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:53:26.000Z","msg":"背可蘭經自保？"},{"pid":"7589b6a22e325d32281c59670eb754cf2a5238f8","tid":497431,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:55:14.000Z","msg"